     <span class="pb center" title="page number in print edition" id="ADMS-06-02-02-pb-0208">[208<a style="padding-left: 0px" onclick="window.open('/img-document-get.xqy?image=ADMS/Pages/ADMS-06-02/ADMS-06-02-02-pb-0208.jpg', 'pageImage', 'scrollbars=1,resizable=1'); return false" onkeypress="this.onclick();" tabindex="0" title="Click to view image of page from print edition"><img src="/img-ML/page-icon.gif" width="18" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;" alt="page icon"/></a>]</span>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA02d083n1-ptr" id="PJA02d083n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Whether a fair copy of this letter was ever sent remains unknown.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA02d083n2-ptr" id="PJA02d083n2">2</a>
      
   <p>Duke of Alva (15081582), Spanish suppressor of revolt in the Low Countries.</p>

